Interface GssFunction

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GssFunctions.AddHsbToCssColor, GssFunctions.AddToNumericValue, GssFunctions.AdjustBrightness, GssFunctions.BaseBlendColors, GssFunctions.BlendColorsHsb, GssFunctions.BlendColorsRgb, GssFunctions.Div, GssFunctions.MakeContrastingColor, GssFunctions.MakeMutedColor, GssFunctions.MakeTranslucent, GssFunctions.MaxValue, GssFunctions.MinValue, GssFunctions.Mult, GssFunctions.SelectFrom, GssFunctions.SubtractFromNumericValue

    public interface GssFunction
    Encapsulates a custom function callable from GSS stylesheet files.
